// @test regression/INV123-udf-tuple-grounded
// @description Tuple-returning UDFs share the same untyped-param grounding path as scalar returns, so destructured elements do not fall back to series<float>.
// @expects errors: 0
//@version=6
indicator("INV123 udf tuple grounded")
pair(p) => [p, close > open]
[txt, cond] = pair("hello")
plot(cond ? close : open)
